snippet.title: Green Hell VR - Co-Op Mode  | Teaser Trailer | Meta Quest Platform
snippet.description:
Here's your first look at the co-op mode for Green Hell VR, coming on Meta Quest 2&3!

Gather your team, ready your tools, and work together in order to survive a hostile and unforgiving jungle when the mode launches in 2024

Get the game here: https://metaque.st/46RhzHY

Join our Discord community not to miss any updates: https://discord.com/invite/greenhell
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/greenhellvr

Thank you for watching; we'll see you in the jungle!
